# CODEOWNERS File for Workflow Protection
#
# This file defines code ownership for critical files and directories.
# It ensures that security-sensitive changes require appropriate review.
#
# Workflow Protection Rules:
# - All workflow changes require security team approval
# - Security configuration files require maintainer review
# - Package and dependency changes require security review
# - Documentation changes require maintainer review
#
# For more information on CODEOWNERS syntax:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

